ãm Hà Nội - Những góc nhìn - 9\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg'%20viewBox%3D'0%200%201200%201835'%2F%3E\" alt=\"Góc riêng về Hà Nội qua triển lãm Hà Nội - Những góc nhìn - 9\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"1835\" data-original=\"https://icdn.dantri.com.vn/2022/10/07/z3781396554617ed1c8ba4a9bcc2e440aacdb99af31e09-1665145686759.jpg\" data-photo-id=\"2167557\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-image\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-image_2167557\" data-content-target=\"/van-hoa/goc-rieng-ve-ha-noi-qua-trien-lam-ha-noi-nhung-goc-nhin-20221007194438781.htm\" data-src=\"https://icdn.dantri.com.vn/thumb_w/680/2022/10/07/z3781396554617ed1c8ba4a9bcc2e440aacdb99af31e09-1665145686759.jpg\"> <figcaption> <p>Tác phẩm \"Hà Nội phố mưa 2\" (Ảnh: Ban Tổ chức).</p> </figcaption></figure> </div>"}